{
  "stem": "8786.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Somebody made a mistake and they all blew up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Hundreds and hundreds of Jewish boys were killed in this way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Today it's a well-known fact.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I'm telling you that there are books about this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "This was one of the most horrible page of the Hungarian anti-Semitism was-- they call it [NON-ENGLISH], or forced labor camps.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto was actually established, as I told you, only the beginning of 1944, when Germans occupied Hungary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Hungarians were asked by Hitler to go and-- they were pressuring them to squeeze the Jewish issue.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Hungarians were cooperating.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They tried for certain times-- they had some prime ministers who were trying to-- to fool a little bit Hitler.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were not as fast with these brutalities as the Germans demanded it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was tough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sure enough, the Germans were not satisfied what the Hungarians did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was not-- they wanted to-- the judenfragen, or the Jewish problem, was not solved yet according to what they would like to have.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Actually, the Germans wanted a total, total destruction or wiping out the Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They did this even in 1945, in April, a few weeks before the liberation that they knew that they are losing, they were still looking for to get rid of the remaining Jews.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So this was not-- had-- had nothing to do with the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was a war against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so the ghetto did not start-- coming back to your question, because you asked me about the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The ghetto period did not start 'til 1944, early part, March.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I think they came in March 19th.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was the time when the Germans occupied Budapest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they ride away like fire.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were all over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were all over, in every little town.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
